REQUIRED
TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=your_telegram_bot_token_here
ACCESS CONTROL (Comma-separated Telegram User IDs allowed to use the bot)
Find your ID using @userinfobot on Telegram
ALLOWED_TELEGRAM_USERS=12345678,98765432
CONCURRENCY CONTROL
MAX_CONCURRENT_TASKS=3
AI EXTRACTION (Get free key at aistudio.google.com)
GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_key_here
CAPTCHA SOLVER (Optional)
CAPSOLVER_API_KEY=your_capsolver_key_here
PROXIES (Optional - for proxy:on command)
PROXY_SERVER=http://pr.oxylab.net:8000
PROXY_USERNAME=your_proxy_user
PROXY_PASSWORD=your_proxy_pass